POLICY-MAP-BG - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-policymgr-oper:policy-manager/global/policy-map/policy-map-types/policy-map-type/{type}/policy-maps/policy-map/{policy-map-name}/policy-map-bg/

Retrieve operation of resource: policy-map-bg

type: string
in path

ID of type

policy-map-name: string
in path

ID of policy-map-name

200 OK
policy-map-bg_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json

CLASS-INFOP - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-policymgr-oper:policy-manager/global/policy-map/policy-map-types/policy-map-type/{type}/policy-maps/policy-map/{policy-map-name}/policy-map-bg/event-infop/policy-event-info-bg/class-infop/

Retrieve operation of resource: class-infop

type: string
in path

ID of type

policy-map-name: string
in path

ID of policy-map-name

200 OK
class-infop_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

                      },
                      
"subs-protocol": {Protocol

                        
"array": "integer" uint8 array

                      },
                      
"mpls-top-label": [MPLS Topmost LABEL

                        {
                          "rng: [
                            {
                              
"max": "integer", Upper limit of the range

                              
"min": "integer" Lower limit of the range

                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ],
                      
"ipv4-acl": {IPv4 Access-list

                        
"string-array": "string" string array

                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              
"type": "string", Class-Map Type QoS/PBR/Netflow/...

              
"description": "string", description

              
"name": "string" Name of the class-map

            }
          ]
        },
        
"num-actions": "integer" num actions

      }
    ]
  }
